title: V - The TV Series Complete (1984)
description:
rapidshare links of my favorite shows:  atilla82-movies blogspot com







V - The TV Series Complete DivX 5.2.1/MP3 CBR 80 kbps. ~220 Meg/ep, no subtitles.

All 19 episodes of the V TV series. Increasingly low budget (re-using the same graphics and film sequences over and over again, killing off main actors as the series ran out of money), but lots of fun.

The TV series comes _after_ the two miniseries:
A) V: The Original Miniseries (2 eps x 90 min)
B) V: The Final Battle (3 eps x 90 minutes)
